---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — MandarinPath"
  description="Terms of service for MandarinPath, an AI-powered Chinese language learning app."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-mandarin-700">Last updated: July 3, 2026</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
      Terms of Service
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
      These terms describe the basic rules for using MandarinPath. By using the service,
      you agree to use it responsibly and in accordance with these terms.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-slate-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Use of the Service</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          MandarinPath provides tools for Chinese language learning, including speaking,
          reading, and writing practice. You are responsible for maintaining the security
          of your account and for activity that occurs through your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          Do not misuse the service, interfere with its operation, attempt unauthorized
          access, upload harmful content, or use MandarinPath in a way that violates
          applicable law or the rights of others.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Learning Feedback</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          MandarinPath may use automated systems to evaluate practice work and provide
          feedback. Feedback is intended for learning support and may not always be
          complete or error-free.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Changes and Availability</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          We may update, suspend, or discontinue parts of the service as MandarinPath
          evolves. We may also update these terms and will post the revised version on
          this page.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7">
          For questions about these terms, contact
          <a class="font-medium text-mandarin-700 hover:text-mandarin-800" href="mailto:support@mandarinpath.com">
            support@mandarinpath.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
